標題: 固態物理（一）（二）Solid Physics
作者: 許世英Open Education Office開放教育推動中心
公開日期: 2006
摘要: 課程首頁
 
本課程是由交通大學電子物理系提供。
 
Phenomena

Mechanica→lstructure、strength 
Thermal→heat capacity、heat conduction、phase transition 
Electrical→insulators、metals、semiconductors、superconductors 
Optical→reflection, refractioncolors 
Magnetic→ferromagnetism 
 
Principles

Newton’s laws 
Maxwell’s EM equations 
Thermodynamics and Statistical mechanics 
Quantum mechanics→Schrodinger equationPauliexclusion principle 
Order and symmetry課程目標/概述  
The purpose of this course is to present a survey of the phenomena exhibited by solid state systems and an introduction to the fundamental physical principles,mathematical concepts, and experimental techniques important in the study of solid state materials. 
 
課程章節




章節

內容

第一章

Crystal structure

第二章

Reciprocal lattice

第三章

Crystal binding and Elastic constants

第四章

Phonon I. Crystal vibrations

第五章

Phonon II, Thermal properties

第六章

Free electron Fermi gas

第七章

Energy bands

第八章

Semiconductor crystals

第九章

Fermi surfaces and Metals

第十章

Superconductivity

第十一章

Diamagnetism and Paramagnetism

第十二章

Ferromagnetism and Antiferromagnetism

 
課程書目


Introduction to Solid State Physics by Charles by Charles Kittel Kittel 8th edition 2004.
 
參考書目

